titles.title: Providing for a joint session of Congress to receive a message from the President.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 415 - 0 (Roll no. 33).

action.text: Ms. Slaughter moved to reconsider the vote.
Mr. Derrick moved to table the motion to reconsider

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 2/17/1993--Introduced. Provides for a joint session of the Congress on February 17, 1993, for a message from the President.
